name": "洞主", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 所以考虑不能无限多的情况，反而应该女孩更多", "timestamp": 1606975507, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 651909, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那种情况的概率很低，所以期望很低，你看看AA的推导呗？", "timestamp": 1606975595, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 651957, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你截断的时后把有限的女男比都记成了无穷，所以应该使女男比更高才对", "timestamp": 1606976568, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 651985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 有限的时候更是对的啊，除非停时的期望无限才会导致男女比不是1", "timestamp": 1606977159, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 651990, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 一个例子是男比女多才停止生", "timestamp": 1606977259, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 651992, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 但是只要生育策略生的数量期望有限，男女比仍然是平衡的", "timestamp": 1606977333, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652000, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 男比女多不在本次讨论范围内", "timestamp": 1606977427, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 停时候的期望无限是啥", "timestamp": 1606977552, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652009, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 是啊", "timestamp": 1606977582, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652016, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不建议这么算好吧，算女生的出现概率更合适,,,按你说的，N不到无穷大，那么按照你文字的截断方式，除了罗列的三种情况外，第四种是三胎都是女生，女男比无穷大，期望无穷大好吧，这不合理，更科学的方式是算截断后出现的男生数和女生数，8个家庭，4个情况1，2个情况2，1个情况3和1个我补充的情况四，男生总数是(4+2+1)*1 = 7个，女生总数是1*2+2*1+3*1 = 7个", "timestamp": 1606977696, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652020, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "乘号消失了,两个数字挨在一起就是相乘\n", "timestamp": 1606977734, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652041, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 我的解法应对我的问题定义是完全合适的。但是求期望的话，有限情况下，确实最后一项的男生为零，确实应该分别算男女合适一点。我回去再验算一下。手里没有纸笔电脑", "timestamp": 1606977974, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652044, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或者你这样想，你打lol或者王者荣耀，有个策略是，每天打到获胜一把或者今天的时间结束了就不玩了，如果每把胜率50%的话，你会有更好的胜率吗？(不太可能", "timestamp": 1606977995, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652049, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 截断问题我再考虑一下", "timestamp": 1606978039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652056, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我不认为是合适的，不应该先列出式子，再去趋向于无穷吗，当那个余项(全女生)是趋于0的话把它扔掉合理，但是由于出现了无穷乘以0的情况，你没有理由直接写出这个无穷和式", "timestamp": 1606978214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652071, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 我这里没有无穷乘0呀", "timestamp": 1606978409, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我的意思是无穷式子来自于有限式子，全女生这一项就是是男女比无穷乘以概率0啊", "timestamp": 1606978621, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652089, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 来自于截断式子的极限", "timestamp": 1606978664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652093, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 不是，你看第一行，我这里没有截断。我的算法解决我的问题是ok的。", "timestamp": 1606978730, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我的意思是无穷应该来自有限情况下的极限，而不应该直接假设无限...在Hans看来假设本身就有问题鸭，就算是你直接假设无穷的情况，那也有概率是0的无穷大男女比啊，这一项直接扔掉不合理啊", "timestamp": 1606978877, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652130, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 696, "w": 700}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1606979051, "type": "image", "url": "yr/yr6rwth3zyljcrq5yvsqbg7qarw4ipjd.jpeg"}, {"cid": 652173, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 就是Hans认为全女生的概率0*无穷大男女比这一项也应该计入...猫猫awsl", "timestamp": 1606979481, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652206, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我前面也想错了。我们考虑这样一个问题，求这种策略下一个家庭的男孩数和女孩数的期望B和G，如果没有次数限制，那男孩女孩的期望都是1；如果限制最多生N个，那么B和G都有减少，B减少的数量是前N次都是女孩的概率乘上接着按照策略生增加的男孩的数量的条件期望，G减少的数量是前N次都是女孩的概率乘上接着按照策略生增加的女孩的数量的条件期望，这两者是相等的，所以有限次还是B=G", "timestamp": 1606979987, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652850, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 859, "w": 1055}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "AA考虑了有限个孩子，和N胎截断，得到仍然是该策略会导致性别比失衡\ndy们AA算的对吗", "timestamp": 1606987699, "type": "image", "url": "rb/rbxmvnrhrg5sdx2ct2rexayywzzt6a27.jpeg"}, {"cid": 652859, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "只要不选择性堕胎，每个新生儿的出生性别都是独立同分布的", "timestamp": 1606987813, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652872, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我们现在讨论的是AA在第一层的论断是否正确", "timestamp": 1606987941, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652967, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: n=1带入发现alice算错了\n", "timestamp": 1606989301, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652977, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 我好像等比数列求和公式算错了", "timestamp": 1606989350, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652978, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Hans退出争论", "timestamp": 1606989366, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 652980, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 结果是B=G=1-0.5^N", "timestamp": 1606989399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653025, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: optional stopping theorem保证了有界的时候男-女期望是0。没必要再白费工夫了", "timestamp": 1606989826, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653040, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 嗯嗯！", "timestamp": 1606989978, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 653058, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 134760, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Grace说的对", "timesta